### Get routes for trains
POST http://localhost:8081/routes/trains
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "origin": "Hamburg Hbf",
  "destination": "Braunschweig Hbf",
  "departureTime": "2026-04-02T08:00:00Z"
}

